--- !u!114 &845651687
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 845651686}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 1fba8f3c0bb9caf4ca1b6aad9f8d1402, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  notes:
  - noteID: 1
    noteText: "DIA 1 - NOVO ESTUDO\n\nProtocolo padr\xE3o de labirinto. Queijo no
      final.\nPaciente R mostra sinais de grande habilidade cognitiva.\n\nDr. Chi
      expressou preocupa\xE7\xE3o com o tempo do teste.\nO comit\xEA espera resultados.\n\n-
      Dra. Tinho"
    triggerRadius: 2
    readOnce: 1
  - noteID: 2
    noteText: "DIA 47 - Paciente R\n\nN\xE3o responde mais a est\xEDmulos. \nN\xE3o
      come mais.\nS\xF3 encara as paredes.\n\n\xC0s vezes acho que ele est\xE1 tentando
      se comunicar conosco.\n\nN\xF3s aumentamos o labirinto.\n\n- Dr. Chen"
    triggerRadius: 2
    readOnce: 1
  - noteID: 3
    noteText: 'Subject R escaped last night.

      Security found it in the observation
      room.

      Just standing there. Watching the monitors.

      Watching the
      other subjects.


      It knows what we''re doing.


      Chen was right.
      We should have stopped.


      - Dr. Morse'
    triggerRadius: 2
    readOnce: 1
  - noteID: 4
    noteText: 'DAY 112


      Subject R''s physiology has changed.

      Limbs
      elongated. Posture altered.

      Something is happening to its mind.


      It''s
      not trying to escape anymore.

      It''s hunting us.


      The maze won''t
      let us leave.


      - Dr. Morse'
    triggerRadius: 2
    readOnce: 1
  - noteID: 5
    noteText: 'DAY 156


      Everyone else is gone.


      Subject R is in the
      walls. I can hear it breathing.


      The doors won''t open. The maze is
      bigger now.

      I don''t remember building these corridors.


      There''s
      cheese at the exit. I can smell it.

      I''m so hungry.


      [The handwriting
      becomes erratic]


      I''m going to run.


      - Dr. Morse'
    triggerRadius: 2
    readOnce: 1
  - noteID: 6
    noteText: 'I''ve been here before.

      I remember writing this.

      I remember
      finding it.


      Subject R was like me once.

      We''re all rats in the
      maze.


      The cheese isn''t real.

      But I can''t stop running.


      Why
      can''t I stop running?'
    triggerRadius: 2
    readOnce: 1
  notePrefab: {fileID: 5744167978809411034, guid: 26f069ba8d336ce43993c334f01da563, type: 3}
  minDistanceBetweenNotes: 10
  minDistanceFromStart: 5
  maxSpawnAttempts: 50
  mazeGenerator: {fileID: 2113078750}
  player: {fileID: 1956618892}
